data.description: This home sits towards the top of Castlewood Estates, with beautiful backyard views of Billings.  Sit on the back covered deck with lighting and ceiling fan or enjoy the second deck from the master bedroom .  This home is fully landscaped, and complete with underground sprinklers and drip system to water the plants on the decks.  The backyard is fully fenced and includes storage for your seasonal items. The home was built by Eaton and Yost. The bedrooms in the basement are large enough for queen or king beds.  Full walk out to covered patio and landscape
